                "type": "stat_block_section",
                "subtype": "special_ability",
                "text": "By making micro-adjustments to their personal gravity, parabolas revivalists can perform impressive feats of acrobatic prowess, even going airborne for short periods of time. While attuned, a parabolas revivalist gains a bonus to Acrobatics checks equal to one-third their CR. While fully attuned, a parabolas revivalist gains the ferocious charge universal creature rule and a fly speed of 30 feet when charging; after they use ferocious charge, they immediately become unattuned.",
